high_descs: Turn around and walk to the microwave next to the oven on the other side of the room.
Pick up the green cup from inside the microwave then close the microwave.
Turn right to face the sink.
Rinse the cup in the sink, then fill the cup with water and then pick the cup up.
Turn left to face the microwave.
Place the green cup inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place the rinsed green cup filled with water back into the microwave.

high_descs: Turn to the left, move to the refrigerator, turn left, move to the counter near the microwave.
Pick up the green cup from in side the microwave.
Turn right and go to the counter in front of the kitchen sink.
Put the green cup in the sink, fill with water, and pick it back up.
Turn left and go to the counter in front of the microwave.
Place the green cup in to the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup full of water in to the microwave.

high_descs: Go straight then take a left to face the microwave.
Open the microwave, remove the green cup from inside, and close the microwave.
Turn to the right to face the sink.
Place the cup in the sink, run the water, turn off the water, and pick up the cup from the sink.
Turn to the left to face the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the cup of water inside, shut the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup full of water in to the microwave.
